<p class="ql-align-center">Hi，又到了故事时间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">准备好跟我一起走进今天的《故事》了吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天，我们要从一个词说起：<strong>朝那湫</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=213190325&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">问题一：怎么读？</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200904/85bf40d3b8084c8ba0a44971b3a9bdcf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200904/9245903ae8a9484683a92467f11c9fb7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>关于“朝那”这两个字的读音</p>
<p>最早的解释是西晋杜预在《春秋左传注疏》中给出的说法</p>
<p>将这两个字读作<strong>zhū nuó，</strong>这种说法后来被宋元时期的官方字典所认可，而“湫”字，在这里读作<strong>jiū</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200904/b33ba5f4a5ef46218a1292d01ee152aa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
